    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="the-posting-cadence"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Spread the 10 pieces across 14 days, not 1 day. Posting everything at once exhausts the topic and burns audience attention. Spaced out, each piece refreshes interest in the hero page and drives a fresh wave of traffic.</p></div></div>
