    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="the-leading-vs-lagging-distinction"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Watch time and indexing rate are leading indicators. They tell you within days whether the content is working. Rankings, citations, and backlinks are lagging indicators. They take 60 to 180 days to move.</p></div></div>
