    <div class="faq-a" id="run-your-video-thought-leadership-program-at-10x-t"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Video thought leadership SEO is the practice of producing expert video content engineered to rank in search engines, earn citations in AI answer engines, and build topical authority in a specific niche. It treats every video as a permanent search asset, not a temporary brand campaign. The core mechanic is pairing the video with a dedicated landing page that contains a transcript-based article, structured data, and internal links.</p></div></div>
